Geotek in marketing pact with IBM . Geotek Communications Inc said Wednesday it had agreed to allow International Business Machines Corp to market Geotek wireless voice and data services nationwide . Under terms of the pact , IBM will market Geoteks services along with its own services , and will provide customer support in all of Geotek ' s U . S . markets , Geotek said . " This agreement will enable us to provide customers with the highest quality products and service as we expand our networks across the U . S . , " Geotek President and Chief Operating Officer Jonathan Crane said in a statement . The agreement is part of a continuing relationship between the two companies . 
